name: X4PRO PAKs 4 Wyse Linux V6
short_description:
PAK add-ons for last version of Dell/Wyse Linux V6 : thin client 5150, S50 and V50

  * rdesktop : 1 PAK version 1.6.0 and 1 PAK version 1.8.3 (last version of rdesktop known to work with Windows(R) 2012 R2)  

     theses PAK embed last version of all necessary libraries include OpenSSL
